history.text: Hello!
Hello, a pleasure to meet you. Feel like going to the movies/
Yes! :D
Have you heard of the movie "The Social Network"?
Wow, I missed it out when it was released. Did you have the chance to watch it?
No I have not, I have heard a bit about it though. It seems interesting!
I wonder what the plot is about...
In the document I have, it says it is a biographical drama about the founding of facebook
Do you use facebook?
Wow, that sounds like a current topic! i use it every now and then; I prefer YouTube
Yes, I prefer instagram. I feel like everyone has a facebook though so it definitely is a relative concept!
Do you know who writes the musical score? I am fond of musicians on film!
I am not sure, it does not say
That's fine. Anyway, I guess it has a lot of drama in it..
Any famous actor or actress there?
Jesse Eisenberg plays the creator of Facebook Mark Zuckerberg, I've never really liked him as an actor, I am curious how he acts in this movie.
Have you heard of Jesse Eisenberg?
Not really.
But I missed an important one. Who's the director?
The director's name is David Fincher
I am not sure what else he directs, do you know?
Jesse Eisenberg was one of the main characters in Zombieland
Wow, that does sound interesting!
I have heard about other David Fincher films, and the only ones coming to my mind are "Alien 3" and "Seven" a crime ovie
excuse me, a crime movie
Ooo those sound intriguing!
Yep. Any reviews of that movie you have heard of?
Well this movie got a Rotten Tomatoes score of 96% but I don't know who is judging through rotten tomatoes because most of the time their reviews do not align with my opinions of movies haha
Lol! That is so right!
It seems to have scored high through other reviewers, it could be worth the view.
Have you heard about how Facebook AI recently created their own language?
i have heard something but have not looked in depth..
But definitely every project they undertake is a breakthrough
So, feel like renting it for this weekend?
It is pretty interesting, I could imagine our world being controlled by artificial intelligence; it seems like the scary direction we are headed towards
Yes!
Thank you for conversing with me! Have a wonderful day!
The same to you. Nice conversing to you, my pleasure!

uid1response.feedback: My chat partner was very active and I think they did not use information that was not available in their document, so I think they did a great job! The movie seems interesting but this guy David Fincher is at times too dark for my taste, but taking into account the topic It might be worth a look!

uid2response.feedback: Thank you for the opportunity to participate in this study!
